@startuml
title Browse/Join Galleries - Full Flow

' ============== ACTORS & COMPONENTS ==============
actor "User" as User
participant "Controller/Input Manager" as Ctrl
participant "HUD" as HUD
participant "Auth Manager" as Sec
participant "Profile Manager" as Prof
participant "Network Manager\n(XRINetworkGameManager\n+ LobbyManager)" as Net
participant "Room Manager" as Room
participant "Canvas" as Canvas
participant "Voice Chat\n(VoiceChatManager/Vivox)" as Voice
participant "Event Logger" as Log

' ============== TRIGGER ==============
User ->> Ctrl : Presses Join
Ctrl ->> HUD : Open "Join a Gallery"
HUD ->> Sec : Check authentication state
Sec --> HUD : Session status (signed-in / guest)
Log ->> Log : Log: HUD.OpenJoin

' ============== LISTING / DIRECTORY ==============
alt Signed-in
  HUD ->> Prof : Fetch managedgallery[] + galleryaccess[]\n(ArtistProfile from Supabase)
  Prof --> HUD : Personal gallery IDs + workspace access list

  HUD ->> Net : GetAllGalleriesAsync()\n(SupabaseGalleryRepository → Supabase DB)
  Net --> HUD : Public GalleryData[] list
else Guest
  HUD ->> Net : GetAllGalleriesAsync()
  Net --> HUD : Public GalleryData[] list
end

HUD --> User : Show: public list + "Enter Code"\n(+ personal/workspace panels if signed-in)

User ->> Ctrl : Selects option
Ctrl ->> HUD : Selection made\n(Public / Personal Workspace / Enter Code)
Log ->> Log : Log: SelectionMade

' ============== FLOW A: Public Gallery via list ============
alt Flow A — Public gallery (from list)
  User ->> Ctrl : Taps a public lobby from list
  Ctrl ->> HUD : JoinLobby(lobby)
  HUD ->> Net : JoinLobbySpecific(lobby)\n→ LobbyManager.SetupRelay()\n→ RelayService.JoinAllocationAsync()
  Net --> HUD : Status: Connecting…

  Net ->> Net : NetworkManager.StartClient()
  Net --> HUD : ConnectionState = Connected
  HUD ->> Room : Load room layout + artworks\n(GalleryData.artworkmap)
  Room ->> Canvas : GetArtworkPaths(galleryId)\n→ signed URLs via Supabase Storage
  Canvas --> Room : Asset refs / streams ready
  Room --> HUD : Gallery rendered

  HUD ->> Voice : Join Vivox channel\n(proximity voice auto-enabled)
  Voice --> User : Voice/chat active
  Log ->> Log : Log: JoinedGallery (public)

  ' ============== FLOW B: Personal Workspace ============
else Flow B — Personal workspace (signed-in only)
  User ->> Ctrl : Selects personal gallery or workspace
  Ctrl ->> HUD : JoinLobby(galleryId from managedgallery[])
  HUD ->> Net : CreateLobby() or JoinLobbySpecific()\n(private lobby, isPrivate=true)
  Net --> HUD : Status: Connecting…

  Net ->> Net : NetworkManager.StartClient()
  Net --> HUD : ConnectionState = Connected
  HUD ->> Room : Load workspace layout + artworks
  Room ->> Canvas : GetArtworkPaths(galleryId)
  Canvas --> Room : Asset refs ready
  Room --> HUD : Workspace rendered

  HUD ->> Voice : Join Vivox channel
  Voice --> User : Voice/chat active
  Log ->> Log : Log: JoinedGallery (workspace)

  ' ============== FLOW C: Private Gallery via Join Code ============
else Flow C — Private gallery (join code)
  User ->> Ctrl : Enter code
  Ctrl ->> HUD : Submit join code
  HUD ->> Net : JoinLobbyByCode(roomCode)\n(LobbyManager → LobbyService.JoinLobbyByCodeAsync())

  alt Code valid / lobby found
    Net ->> Net : SetupRelay(lobby)\n→ RelayService.JoinAllocationAsync()\n→ SetClientRelayData()
    Net ->> Net : NetworkManager.StartClient()
    Net --> HUD : ConnectionState: Authenticating → Connecting → Connected
    HUD ->> Room : Load room layout + artworks
    Room ->> Canvas : GetArtworkPaths(galleryId)
    Canvas --> Room : Signed asset URLs ready
    Room --> HUD : Gallery rendered

    HUD ->> Voice : Join Vivox channel
    Voice --> User : Voice/chat active
    Log ->> Log : Log: JoinedGallery (code)

  else Code invalid / lobby not found
    Net --> HUD : LobbyServiceException\n("Lobby not found")
    HUD --> User : Show error: "Lobby not found.\nPlease try a new code."
    Log ->> Log : Log: JoinFailed (invalid code)
  end

end

' ============== NOTES ==============
note over Net
Networking stack:
Unity Lobby + Relay (via LobbyManager)
NGO NetworkManager (XRMultiplayer)
Connection states:
None → Authenticating → Authenticated
→ Connecting → Connected
end note

note over Voice
VoiceChatManager uses Vivox.
Proximity (3D spatial) voice is
distance-based and auto-enabled
on join. Text chat also available.
end note

note over Room, Canvas
Postcondition: gallery/workspace
rendered with artworks loaded from
Supabase Storage via signed URLs.
GalleryData.artworkmap[slot → artworkId]
drives Canvas placement.
end note

@enduml
